s are the best solution for your unique situation.\r\n<h4>What is commercial use?</h4>\r\nYour personal auto insurance will exclude coverage for commercial uses of your vehicle.  That is why it is important to discuss your needs with us, so that in case of an accident, there is no chance of being uninsured.\r\n\r\nWhat can be done to lower the cost of commercial auto insurance?\r\n\r\nThe following strategies can generally help to lower the cost of your insurance coverage:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Anti-theft and safety devices</strong> – items such as alarms, GPS tracking, and air bags can lower your premiums.  In addition, programs which require seat belt usage can also help reduce your costs.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Deductibles</strong> – deductibles represent the portion of risk you are willing to absorb before the insurance company would pay on a claim.  The higher the deductible, the lower your premiums will be.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Driver records</strong> – by hiring only qualified drivers with safe driving records, you can significantly reduce your premiums.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Location</strong> - determines premiums for the theft portion of your insurance coverage.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Vehicles</strong> – the sportier the car, generally the higher the premium.  By having 5 star safely rated vehicles, you can significantly reduce your premiums.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Other Considerations</h4>\r\nCertain types of businesses are subject to federal and state regulations in the operation of their vehicles.  It is important to fully understand those regulations.  We can help you, to ensure you are in compliance.  In addition, it is important if your company will be using the equipment of third parties, such as leased or rental equipment: if so, you will need non-owned vehicle coverage.  We are happy to help you ensure you are in compliance and have the appropriate level of coverage for your business.'),(1009,18,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_content','field_54208212716c9'),(1010,18,'section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','null'),(1011,18,'_section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','field_54208529716cb'),(1012,18,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','null'),(1013,18,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','field_542086b2716cd'),(1014,18,'section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content',''),(1015,18,'_section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content','field_542085ae716cc'),(1016,18,'section_0_page_builder','1'),(1017,18,'_section_0_page_builder','field_54207e5048901'),(1018,18,'_thumbnail_id','110'),(1019,19,'_thumbnail_id','110'),(1020,19,'section_0_section_background_color','white-bg'),(1021,19,'_section_0_section_background_color','field_53c437928d74b'),(1022,19,'section_0_section_text_color','black-text'),(1023,19,'_section_0_section_text_color','field_73c489928d74b'),(1024,19,'section_0_section_title','Worker\'s Compensation'),(1025,19,'_section_0_section_title','field_54111e5786402'),(1026,19,'section_0_section_class',''),(1027,19,'_section_0_section_class','field_54111e9986402'),(1028,19,'section_0_section_title_color','null'),(1029,19,'_section_0_section_title_color','field_73gg89928d74b'),(1030,19,'section_0_section_background_image',''),(1031,19,'_section_0_section_background_image','field_53c438868d74c'),(1032,19,'section_0_fixed_image',''),(1033,19,'_section_0_fixed_image','field_542555ae716cc'),(1034,19,'section_0_no_row',''),(1035,19,'_section_0_no_row','field_799555ae716cc'),(1036,19,'section_0_equalize_columns',''),(1037,19,'_section_0_equalize_columns','field_142000ae722cc'),(1038,19,'section_0_section_padding','pd75'),(1039,19,'_section_0_section_padding','field_53c432228d74b'),(1040,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_size','medium-12'),(1041,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_size','field_54207e5748902'),(1042,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_class',''),(1043,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_class','field_54111e5748902'),(1044,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_alignment','left'),(1045,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_alignment','field_54333180716c8'),(1046,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_background_image',''),(1047,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_background_image','field_53c438333d74c'),(1048,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_background','null'),(1049,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_background','field_54208481716ca'),(1050,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_title',''),(1051,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_title','field_54207f3b48904'),(1052,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_title_alignment','text-left'),(1053,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_title_alignment','field_54208180716c8'),(1054,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_image',''),(1055,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_image','field_54207ee248903'),(1056,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_content','Worker\'s compensation insurance provides protection for both the employee and employer and brings stability to the workplace.  The purpose of workers’ compensation insurance is to provide employees with proper compensation for job-related injuries or illnesses. Although specific laws vary by state, workers\' compensation insurance is generally required of companies with W-2 employees.\r\n\r\nMany states use the standards of the National Council of Compensation Insurance to determine the rates of their workers’ compensation insurance. The NCCI, a non-governmental, private organization, uses classifications to determine the risk factors involved in particular jobs. The risk factor will obviously be greater with occupations such as mining and construction, and generally low for clerical workers.\r\n\r\nPremiums are usually determined through a formula which includes a number of factors including salary, bonuses and other variables.  A remuneration number is then determined and is used in conjunction with the risk factor classification of the job to arrive at the cost of the insurance. Premiums can also be adjusted by “experience modification factors”, which are standards set by the NCCI and other organizations for reducing premiums based on a company’s loss history.\r\n\r\nThe initial premiums are based on a number of estimates including the amount of wages to be paid to workers.  At the end of the policy period an audit is performed to determine the actual premium amount.  The results of the audit can result in either a refund or additional premiums due.\r\n\r\nOur team of professionals are highly experienced and knowledgeable in helping you develop a cost effective worker\'s compensation strategy.'),(1057,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_content','field_54208212716c9'),(1058,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','null'),(1059,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','field_54208529716cb'),(1060,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','null'),(1061,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','field_542086b2716cd'),(1062,19,'section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content',''),(1063,19,'_section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content','field_542085ae716cc'),(1064,19,'section_0_page_builder','1'),(1065,19,'_section_0_page_builder','field_54207e5048901'),(1066,20,'_thumbnail_id','110'),(1067,20,'section_0_section_background_color','white-bg'),(1068,20,'_section_0_section_background_color','field_53c437928d74b'),(1069,20,'section_0_section_text_color','black-text'),(1070,20,'_section_0_section_text_color','field_73c489928d74b'),(1071,20,'section_0_section_title','Cyber Liability'),(1072,20,'_section_0_section_title','field_54111e5786402'),(1073,20,'section_0_section_class',''),(1074,20,'_section_0_section_class','field_54111e9986402'),(1075,20,'section_0_section_title_color','null'),(1076,20,'_section_0_section_title_color','field_73gg89928d74b'),(1077,20,'section_0_section_background_image',''),(1078,20,'_section_0_section_background_image','field_53c438868d74c'),(1079,20,'section_0_fixed_image',''),(1080,20,'_section_0_fixed_image','field_542555ae716cc'),(1081,20,'section_0_no_row',''),(1082,20,'_section_0_