(1519,29,'_section_0_page_builder_0_title_alignment','field_54208180716c8'),(1520,29,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_image',''),(1521,29,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_image','field_54207ee248903'),(1522,29,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_content','Transportation risks are some of the most complex insurance risks there are due to various filings and regulations.  Our team can assist you in navigating the confusing maze of regulations and filings to assist your business and help ensure your success.\r\n\r\n<strong>Highlight of Insurance Coverages Available</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Truckers Primary Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Non-Trucking (Bobtail) Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Truckers Physical Damage</li>\r\n	<li>Motor Truck Cargo</li>\r\n	<li>Trailer Interchange</li>\r\n	<li>Workers Compensation</li>\r\n	<li>General Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Property Coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Excess/Umbrella Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Occupational Accident</li>\r\n	<li>Warehouse Legal Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Lease/Loan Gap Coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Contingent Cargo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Vehicles</strong> – there are a lot of different types of vehicles.  Here is a sample list – but certainly not all inclusive – of the vehicles we insure.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tractor/Trailer</li>\r\n	<li>Straight Truck</li>\r\n	<li>Dump Truck</li>\r\n	<li>Flatbed Truck</li>\r\n	<li>Refrigeration</li>\r\n	<li>Hot Shot</li>\r\n	<li>Tow Truck</li>\r\n	<li>Garbage Truck</li>\r\n	<li>Cargo Van</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSome of the Insurance Coverages We Offer\r\n\r\nTexas Truck Liability insurance\r\n\r\nThis is usually the most costly portion of any trucking company\'s insurance package. Protecting you from damage or injuries to other people as a result of truck accidents, this coverage is also mandated by the State and Federal agencies and a form of proof is required to be sent to them.\r\n\r\nGeneral Liability Insurance\r\n\r\nAs the name implies, this coverage pertains to very broad coverage. Protection for injuries or property damage sustained while on your premises, using your products or services, or because of a breach of contract are some of the more customary types of risk this coverage is intended for.\r\n\r\nMotor Truck Cargo Insurance\r\n\r\nThe transporter of freight and commodities assumes responsibility for the cargo they have taken control of. The amount of that responsibility should be clearly established and understood by both the shipper and the transporter before the shipment is moved. This is usually done by contract, by bill of lading disclosure, or by published tariffs. Unfortunately, this level of detail is often overlooked by both parties.\r\n\r\nContact <a href=\"mailto:info@weinsure4you.com\">info@weinsure4you.com</a> to get in touch with a transportation specialist on our team.'),(1523,29,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_content','field_54208212716c9'),(1524,29,'section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','null'),(1525,29,'_section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','field_54208529716cb'),(1526,29,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','null'),(1527,29,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','field_542086b2716cd'),(1528,29,'section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content',''),(1529,29,'_section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content','field_542085ae716cc'),(1530,29,'section_0_page_builder','1'),(1531,29,'_section_0_page_builder','field_54207e5048901'),(1532,30,'section_0_section_background_color','white-bg'),(1533,30,'_section_0_section_background_color','field_53c437928d74b'),(1534,30,'section_0_section_text_color','black-text'),(1535,30,'_section_0_section_text_color','field_73c489928d74b'),(1536,30,'section_0_section_title','Technology'),(1537,30,'_section_0_section_title','field_54111e5786402'),(1538,30,'section_0_section_class',''),(1539,30,'_section_0_section_class','field_54111e9986402'),(1540,30,'section_0_section_title_color','null'),(1541,30,'_section_0_section_title_color','field_73gg89928d74b'),(1542,30,'section_0_section_background_image',''),(15