s the market strength our clients need in order to compete in today’s business environment.\r\n<h2>Positional Excellence</h2>\r\nAs an <strong>independent agent</strong>, we represent many nationally recognized insurance companies. We can provide proposals from various insurance companies to find the best possible rate with the best coverage. We will consult with you to understand your needs before recommending the best combination of coverage and value for your unique situation.\r\n<h2>Exceptional Service</h2>\r\nWe will:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Identify the insurance services that are right for you</li>\r\n	<li>Guide you through the claims process for a quick and fair resolution</li>\r\n	<li>Counsel you on matters related to your coverage or account</li>\r\n	<li>Provide prompt service with a unique personal touch</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe will partner with you to provide the needed product—we will be a resource you can count on to look out for your best interests.\r\n<h2>Recognized Leader</h2>\r\nWeatherby - Eisenrich Insurance has been highlighted by several insurance publications. We work with most national insurance companies including Allstate, Safeco, Travelers, Met Life Home &amp; Auto, Liberty Mutual, Nationwide and many more. We are members of Combined Agents of America, Trusted Choice, Independent Insurance Agents of Texas and have been recognized as an IIABA Best Practices Agency year after year. In 2013, we received the Top Performing Agency in Size Class by Best Practices.\r\n<h2>THE WE DIFFERENCE:</h2>\r\nWE approach the client and their needs in a <strong>professional</strong> and <strong>understanding</strong> way. Insurance has become a necessity in life and business. WE aim to make the process as positive for the client as possible.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ease of doing business</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledgeable</li>\r\n	<li>Resourceful</li>\r\n	<li>Committed</li>\r\n	<li>Caring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur customer service approach incorporates our core values shared by our entire staff. We are dedicated to providing a <strong>team approach</strong> to provide our client with the highest level of responsiveness and knowledge. Our aim is to respond to your needs with\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Excellence</li>\r\n	<li>Enthusiasm</li>\r\n	<li>Energy</li>\r\n	<li>Ethics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur strengths, perspective, and commitment make us an excellent partner for your insurance needs.'),(1615,10,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_content','field_54208212716c9'),(1616,10,'section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','null'),(1617,10,'_section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','field_54208529716cb'),(1618,10,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','null'),(1619,10,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','field_542086b2716cd'),(1620,10,'section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content',''),(1621,10,'_section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content','field_542085ae716cc'),(1622,10,'section_0_page_builder','1'),(1623,10,'_section_0_page_builder','field_54207e5048901'),(1624,111,'_wp_attached_file','2015/05/About-Us-Banner.jpg'),(1625,111,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1280;s:6:\"height\";i:250;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2015/05/About-Us-Banner.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"About-Us-Banner-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:26:\"About-Us-Banner-300x59.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:59;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"About-Us-Banner-1024x200.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:200;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"featured-thumb\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"About-Us-Banner-640x250.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:640;s:6:\"height\";i:250;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\