sider include, if your spouse is working, would you want to provide college funding for your children and possible estate taxes.\r\n\r\nWe take the time to understand your needs to determine the amount of insurance appropriate for your unique situation.  We then can recommend different insurance product options to fit both your needs and your budget.\r\n\r\nTo assist you in determing the the amount and pricing of a life policy contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@weinsure4you.com\">info@weinsure4you.com</a> , click on this <a href=\"http://www.lifehappens.org/life-insurance-needs-calculator/\">life calculator</a> to get started on a plan for your future protection.'),(2152,36,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_content','field_54208212716c9'),(2153,36,'section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','null'),(2154,36,'_section_0_page_builder_0_content_background','field_54208529716cb'),(2155,36,'section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','null'),(2156,36,'_section_0_page_builder_0_column_link','field_542086b2716cd'),(2157,36,'section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content',''),(2158,36,'_section_0_page_builder_0_vertically_center_content','field_542085ae716cc'),(2159,36,'section_0_page_builder','1'),(2160,36,'_section_0_page_builder','field_54207e5048901'),(2161,44,'_thumbnail_id','108'),(2162,44,'section_0_section_background_color','white-bg'),(2163,44,'_section_0_section_background_color','field_53c437928d74b'),(2164,44,'section_0_section_text_color','black-text'),(2165,44,'_section_0_section_text_color','field_73c489928d74b'),(2166,44,'section_0_section_title','Careers'),(2167,44,'_section_0_section_title','field_54111e5786402'),(2168,44,'section_0_section_class',''),(2169,44,'_section_0_section_class','field_54111e9986402'),(2170,44,'section_0_section_title_color','null'),(2171,44,'_section_0_section_title_color','field_73gg89928d74b'),(2172,44,'section_0_section_background_image',''),(2173,44,'_section_0_section_background_image','field_53c438868d74c'),(2174,44,'sectio