ed.</li>\r\n	<li>Commit our staff to continuing education so they may be more knowledgeable in serving you.</li>\r\n	<li>Treat you with respect and courtesy.</li>\r\n	<li>Conduct our business in an ethical manner.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis is our 100% Pledge of Performance to you. If we fail in any way to meet this commitment, please let us know immediately, and we will make every effort possible to meet and exceed your expectations as quickly as possible\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.trustedchoice.com/\">www.trustedchoice.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Independent Insurance Agents of Texas ( IIAT )</strong>\r\n\r\nIIAT is a nonprofit organization of 1,700 independent property and casualty insurance agency members and 250 associate members from insurance companies, MGAs and other vendors of agency products. Their total member agency employee population is more than 12,000.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.iiat.org/\">www.iiat.org</a>'),(2354,13,'_section_0_page_builder_4_column_content','field_54208212716c9'),(2355,13,'section_0_page_builder_4_content_background','null'),(2356,13,'_section_0_page_builder_4_content_background','field_54208529716cb'),(2357,13,'section_0_page_builder_4_column_link','null'),(2358,13,'_section_0_page_builder_4_column_link','field_542086b2716cd'),(2359,13,'section_0_page_builder_4_vertically_center_content',''),(2360,13,'_section_0_page_builder_4_vertically_center_content','field_542085ae716cc'),(2361,13,'section_0_page_builder','5'),(2362,13,'_section_0_page_builder','field_54207e5048901'),(2363,120,'_wp_attached_file','2015/06/commercial.jpg'),(2364,120,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:640;s:6:\"height\";i:640;s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"2015/06/commercial.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"commercial-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"commercial-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"heig